In 2-gallon zipper-type storage bag, combine KELLOGG'S CRISPIX cereal, pretzels and peanuts. Set aside. Mix together sugar and spices. Set aside. Combine oil, Worcestershire sauce and liquid smoke. Mix well. Pour oil mixture over cereal mixture. Close bag and gently toss until evenly coated. Add spice mixture and close bag. Gently toss until evenly coated. Store in airtight container.